555
00:40:39,380 --> 00:40:41,139
I'm not blaming you.

556
00:40:41,139 --> 00:40:44,219
You're young and inexperienced.

557
00:40:47,479 --> 00:40:49,270
Sheng Juan,

558
00:40:50,340 --> 00:40:54,090
