I'm not worried about our Qiao Xi.

562
00:41:10,860 --> 00:41:12,459
Since he's a boy.

563
00:41:12,459 --> 00:41:15,559
And he's popular with female classmates at school.

564
00:41:15,559 --> 00:41:20,380
